room_title: Escape room "Malice Manor" by EscapeOut Folsom in Sacramento
room_description: Secrets can be hidden, but never destroyed. This was the harsh lesson learned by the members of the Randle family, whose cursed bloodline came to a tragic and mysterious end nearly a hundred years ago. Since then, tales of ghostly voices, doors that open themselves, and visions of a little girl have haunted the home. Now itâ€™s up to you to unravel the mysteries of the child whose soul remains trapped there.
